overview: If you love great hockey action, then Don Cherry's Rock' em Sock' em 23 is a must for your DVD collection. All the best NHL 2010/11 highlights from the greatest saves, hits, goals and bloopers are all here on one DVD. Don also takes a look back at the 2011 Stanley Cup Playoffs, including Boston's seven game victory over Vancouver. We also included the best of Coach's Corner and more. Rock' em Sock' em 23 - it just keeps getting better.
tagline: Highlights from the 2010-2011 NHL season. Narrated by Don Cherry.
title: Don Cherry's Rock'em Sock'em Hockey 23
